dct_title_s: Germany, all industries : net production values by states and provinces, 1936.
dct_description_sm: No relief shown. Shows net production values by states and provinces from 1936 with boundaries of report area and province, state, and international boundaries. "From: Reichsamt für Wehrwirtschaftliche Planung 'Die Deutsche Industrie: Gersamtergebnisse [sic] der Amtlichen produktions Statistik', Berlin, 1939." "Confidential." "No. 3886 - R & A, OSS, August 12, 1944."
dct_creator_sm: United States. Office of Strategic Services. Research and Analysis Branch
